transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra, this is Olivia speaking.

Speaker 2: Who do I have the pleasure of speaking with today?

Speaker 1: Joshua Fisher.

Speaker 2: Hi, Joshua, how are you?

Speaker 1: I'm good.

Speaker 2: I'm calling because I just noticed I had a subscription come across again.

Speaker 1: I canceled my subscription a while back.

Speaker 2: Okay, I can look into this for you.

Speaker 1: What is your date of birth, Joshua?

Speaker 2: It's April 8, 1979.

Speaker 1: Okay, great.

Speaker 2: Yeah, so this refill from today, you do not need it, is that right?

Speaker 1: Correct.

Speaker 2: Okay, give me one moment.

Speaker 1: Okay, so I just canceled and refunded that order, so you should see that refund back very soon.

Speaker 2: Yeah, so if you don't want to receive those regular monthly refills with your prescription,

Speaker 1: you certainly don't have to.

Speaker 2: You always have the option to place your prescription on hold for up to six months at a time,

Speaker 1: just because six months is when the prescription would expire if we didn't refill it.

Speaker 2: And the way that would work is if you did want to order during that duration of time, you could.

Speaker 1: You just have to give us a call to place the order yourself.

Speaker 2: Okay, yeah, I tried to go on a while back when I went on the line to try to do it.

Speaker 1: That's why I called in last time because when I went online,

Speaker 2: it doesn't give me the option to do any of that anymore, to hold it or to cancel it or anything.

Speaker 1: Yeah, yeah, I am sorry about that.

Speaker 2: But, yeah, I mean, I took care of that monthly refill and placed the prescription on hold for you.

Speaker 1: So if you do need anything before the end of July, just give us a call to place the order yourself.

Speaker 2: We're always here Monday through Friday, 8 to 5 Pacific.

Speaker 1: Okay, cool.

Speaker 2: Appreciate that.

Speaker 1: Thank you.

Speaker 2: Yeah, of course.

Speaker 1: I hope you have a great day, Josh.

Speaker 2: Thanks, you too.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye.

Speaker 2: Yeah, bye.
